lass="to-do-children-unchecked">DRP1: Backups of Databases</span></li></ul><ul id="158bb207-c35f-41e1-ac83-68a8da80e450" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> <span class="to-do-children-unchecked">DRP2: Infrastructure can be recreated through checklists / IaaC</span></li></ul><ul id="c5789eda-2e54-45b8-a516-88978e484199" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> <span class="to-do-children-unchecked">DRP3: Projects / Accounts separated per team</span></li></ul><ul id="d4c02704-107a-4040-bf79-0ee5759693e1" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> <span class="to-do-children-unchecked">DRP4+: As business needs dictate.</span></li></ul><h1 id="f3b6e4a9-7e26-4804-9785-c9fc227c3680" class="">Cost Optimization / Performance Engineering</h1><h2 id="d6f13b70-111d-44b4-a0a8-984a220f9072" class="">Cloud Costs</h2><ul id="3dfad286-ccb3-4e71-964c-868a30b9c57b" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> <span class="to-do-children-unchecked">Cost0: Use those free tier credits!!</span></li></ul><ul id="2a78905b-2887-4a7e-9af7-26b101b94c33" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> <span class="to-do-children-unchecked">Cost1: Rightsize assets to meet workload and scalability requirements. Make Costs visible (monitoring) to avoid surprises.</span></li></ul><ul id="4aa02076-d534-46d6-bf9b-ce8c52cbb143" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> <span class="to-do-children-unchecked">Cost2: Use baseline to negotiate pre-spend agreements (AWS).</span></li></ul><ul id="8bd12be6-6d86-4879-9755-07ccdb321ea5" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> <span class="to-do-children-unchecked">Cost3: Cloud Cost Engineer hired. Team leaders report on a regular basis their cloud cost, and attribute changes.</span></li></ul><ul id="01f363ae-3832-4eb0-bd01-73aa58c2ab50" class="to-do-list"><li><div class="checkbox checkbox-off"></div> 